name: Greaterthan1
tagline: A Bukkit plugin made for fun
body:
This is the main page for the Greater Than 1 mod of Bukkit.
This plugin is still in development, and is pretty much useless now.
By the way, the plugin is done in Eclipse 3.8, and has no external dependencies (for now >:3).
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
